					"type": 23,
					"value": "Interacting with the console just displays camera footage of the hostages locations, focusing on Ravengard if present first, then Omeluum if present, and then the rest of the hostages.\r\n\r\nThe dialog is repeatable and can be accessed during the whole situation."
